            <li>client-side and server-side validation</li>
            <li>customizible container placement</li>
            <li>toggle by click, dblclick or manually</li>
            <li>keyboard support (escape/enter/tab)</li>                            
            <li>works in IE7+ and all modern browsers</li>                            
            <li>unit tested</li>                            
            <li>live events</li>                            
        </ul>        
